---
layout: base.njk
title: Garden
permalink: /blog/
---

<header class="page-header">
  <p class="eyebrow">Garden archive</p>
  <h1>Notes, logs, and experiments</h1>
  <p class="page-intro">
    A chronological view of the public research desk: polished notes, small demos,
    and eventually the rougher log entries that trace how ideas develop.
  </p>
  <nav class="archive-jump" aria-label="Archive filters">
    <a href="/tags/notes/">Notes</a>
    <a href="/tags/experiments/">Experiments</a>
    <a href="/tags/meta/">Meta</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
  <li class="post-list-item">
    <div class="post-list-meta">
      <span class="post-kind">{{ post.data.kind or "note" }}</span>
      <time class="post-list-date">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</time>
      {% if post.data.status %}
        <span class="post-status">{{ post.data.status }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-list-title">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    {% if post.data.summary %}
      <p class="post-list-summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
    {% endif %}
    {% if post.data.tags %}
    <span class="post-tags">
      {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
        {% if tag != "posts" %}
          <a href="/tags/{{ tag }}/" class="tag">{{ tag }}</a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </span>
    {% endif %}
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
